-- DBS Hires ex-RBS Banker Rogerio Bernardo for Bond Syndicate Team
-- B y   T a n y a   A n g e r e r
-- 2013-10-16T04:59:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-16/dbs-hires-ex-rbs-banker-rogerio-bernardo-for-bond-syndicate-team.html
DBS Group Holdings has hired Rogerio
Bernardo as part of its bond syndicate team in  Singapore ,
according to an e-mailed statement from Clifford Lee, the bank’s
head of fixed-income.
*Bernardo was previously at Royal Bank of Scotland Group as a
director in its Asia-Pacific bond syndicate team
*At DBS, he will be a senior vice president, supporting the
bank’s primary deal activities in the region, and report to Lee:
statement  To contact the reporter on this story:
